    <string name="help"><![CDATA[<b>How to create a post</b>
        <ol>
            <li>Press the create button</li>
            <li>On a dialog box select either <i>Devotion</i>, <i>Poems</i>  or <i>Stories</i> </li>
            <li>Follow the instructions in the editor</li>
        </ol>

        <p>
        <b>How to upload to post</b>
        <ol>
            <li>If in the editor press the <i>POST</i> button in the appbar, else</li>
            <li>Press account > select <i>Devotion</i>, <i>Poems</i>  or <i>Stories</i> </li>
            <li>Select appropriate item</li>
            <li>Press <i>POST</i></li>
        </ol>
        </p>

        <p>
        <b>How to delete from My Block</b>
        <ol>
            <li>If in the editor press the <i>menu icon</i> in the appbar and then <i>delete</i>, else</li>
            <li>Press account > select <i>Devotion</i>, <i>Poems</i>  or <i>Stories</i> </li>
            <li>Select appropriate item</li>
            <li>Press <i>delete</i></li>
        </ol>
        </p>
        <b>How to delete Posted items</b>
        <ol>
            <li>If in the editor press the <i>menu icon</i> in the appbar and then <i>delete</i>, else</li>
            <li>Press account > select <i>Devotion</i>, <i>Poems</i>  or <i>Stories</i> from the posted section </li>
            <li>Select appropriate item</li>
            <li>Press the <i>delete</i> icon</li>
        </ol>
        </p>

        <p>
        <b>How to update post from My Block</b>
        <ol>
            <li>If in the editor press the <i>POST</i> button in the appbar and follow instructions else</li>
            <li>Press account > select <i>Devotion</i>, <i>Poems</i>  or <i>Stories</i> </li>
            <li>Select appropriate item</li>
            <li>Repeat 1</li>
        </ol>
        </p>

        <p>
        <b>How to update Stories from Posted</b>
        <ol>
            <li>If in the editor press the <i>POST</i> button in the appbar and follow instructions else</li>
            <li>Press account > select <i>Stories</i> </li>
            <li>Select appropriate story</li>
            <li>Press button 1 to change category</li>
            <li>Press button 2 to change story status</li>
            <li>Press button 3 and to either</li>
            <ol>
                <li>Add Chapter</li>
                <li>Edit Chapter</li>
                <li>Edit Description</li>
                <li>Edit Title</li>
            </ol>
        </ol>
        </p>
]]>
    </string>
